data.description: Nestled on a generous 7,540 sqft corner lot, this delightful 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home invites you into a warm and welcoming atmosphere. Boasting a 2-car garage, it offers both convenience and security, while the spacious outdoor area is perfect for gardening, entertaining, or enjoying the fresh air. With 1,066 sqft of interior living space, this cozy residence is ideally suited for family living, with the option to convert a bedroom into a home office or playroom. Located in a friendly Montclair neighborhood, you're close to excellent schools, shopping, dining, and parks, making this an ideal place to call home. Additionally, its proximity to the 10 freeway ensures easy access to nearby areas, adding to the property's convenience and desirability. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or an investor seeking potential, this property offers a solid foundation for comfortable living and future growth. Don't miss the chance to make 5032 Orchard St your own and experience the joys of homeownership in this desirable location.
